It sounds like a hoax, like that mmorpg &quot;Dawn&quot; that actually got people to believe it would exist.<br>
<br>
Even if its not a hoax, it won't matter. A system could come out that cost 100 bucks and was 150 times more powerful than xbox or playstation 2, but it would not sell a single game or get retail shelf space. In order to do so it would have to be an already existing large brand with products in many store, such as Microsoft.<br>
<br>
It would also have to get gamemakers on board, which is only possible if you are a proven player like Sony or Nintendo or a proven entity like Microsoft.<br>
<br>
